+## doctor
+
+Checks local Pala Memory Core systems and prints what is ready, missing, or optional.
+
+```text
+python pala.py doctor
+```
+
+Machine-readable output:
+
+```text
+python pala.py doctor --json
+```
+
+Useful options:
+
+| Option | Purpose |
+|---|---|
+| `--knowledge-bank C:\path\to\repo` | Check a custom knowledge-bank repo path |
+| `--drive-target C:\path\to\Drive` | Check a custom Drive-folder backup target |
+| `--strict` | Exit non-zero if a required check fails |
+
 ## list
 
 Lists saved records from the local vault.
