+# v0.12 System Doctor
+
+Date: 2026-06-09
+Phase: system doctor preview
+Status: PASS for local system health report
+
+## Goal
+
+Give users one command that explains which Pala Memory Core systems are ready, optional, or missing on the current machine.
+
+## Added Behavior
+
+| Area | Change |
+|---|---|
+| CLI | Added `python pala.py doctor` |
+| JSON | Added `python pala.py doctor --json` |
+| Paths | Supports custom `--knowledge-bank` and `--drive-target` |
+| Strict mode | Supports `--strict` for required failures |
+| Coverage | Checks 10+ systems across local storage, records, files, dashboard, recovery, ChatGPT import, mobile, browser, GitHub, knowledge bank, Drive, and optional Playwright |
+
+## Command
+
+```powershell
+python .\pala.py doctor
+python .\pala.py doctor --json
+```
+
+## Smoke Test
+
+Executed in `C:\Users\Pala-Home-1\Desktop\Codex\pala-memory-core`:
+
+```powershell
+python -m py_compile .\pala.py
+python .\pala.py doctor
+python .\pala.py doctor --json
+```
+
+Observed key output:
+
+```text
+Pala Memory Core Doctor
+active_systems=12 pass=16 warn=2 fail=0
+PASS | runtime          | Python runtime | 3.12.10
+PASS | local-storage    | Local data folders | ready
+PASS | memory-records   | Record vault | records=8
+PASS | files            | Attachment files | attachments=2 missing=0
+PASS | dashboard        | Dashboard shell | dashboard\index.html
+PASS | recovery         | Recovery CLI | list/search/show commands are registered
+PASS | chatgpt          | ChatGPT export importer | zip/folder/json/html/md/txt import path is registered
+PASS | mobile           | Mobile share watcher | watch mobile-share command is registered
+PASS | browser          | Browser URL capture | stdlib urllib capture path is registered
+WARN | browser          | Playwright capture | optional dependency missing; install with python -m pip install playwright
+PASS | github           | GitHub CLI auth | gh auth status ok
+PASS | knowledge-bank   | Knowledge-bank repo | C:\Users\Pala-Home-1\Desktop\Codex\pala-os-bilgi-bankasi
+WARN | drive            | Drive folder target | not created yet: C:\Users\Pala-Home-1\Documents\Pala Memory Core Drive Backup
+```
+
+## Release Posture
+
+This is a setup/readiness preview. It does not install missing optional dependencies or create cloud integrations automatically. It makes the local system state visible so users and agents can decide the next action quickly.
